MICROVIEW TECHNO said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 50.87% to NT$98,620,000 from NT$200,753,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             98,620          200,753    
YOY%             -50.87%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,330,527        2,681,156   
YOY%             -13.08% 
=================================================================
 